highlights.text: “零距离的思念” by TINY 7 has been on Viral Songs Malaysia the longest, at 139 days straight.
Anirudh Ravichander has the most spots on Viral Songs Malaysia. “Kokki” is the highest at #15.
“Kutukan Mantan” by Manda Fvnky is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs Malaysia, up 36 spots at #61.
“竈門禰豆子のうた -full ver.-” by Go Shiina	 and Nami Nakagawa is the highest new entry on Viral Songs Malaysia at #27.
